brainly_data.question: Jada drank 12 oz of water from her bottle. This is 60% of the water the bottle holds. How much water does the bottle hold?
brainly_data.subject: Mathematics

all_answers.question: Jada drank 12 oz of water from her bottle. This is 60% of the water the bottle holds. How much water does the bottle hold?
all_answers.subject: Mathematics
all_answers.text: The answer is 60 percent of 12 and the word of means to multiply so 60% of 12 equals the sum of 7.2 or 7%
